{"type": "article", "id": 27541, "title": "肥皂泡吊灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-31T07:01:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702142438nNGBmo8ESKjRT49w.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>还记得小时候和朋友一起玩吹泡泡的游戏吗，你是否想过把美丽的泡泡们留住？Sebastian Scherer 为 Neo/Craft 设计的吊灯 <a href=\"http://en.neocraft.com/product/iris/\">Iris</a> 是一款获得 2016 德国设计奖的作品，Scherer 以肥皂泡作为灵感，采用纯人工吹制的方法制作而成。为了还原出泡泡在阳光下的颜色，Iris 内部附着了一层彩虹膜，光线透过灯罩时就会产生奇妙的光影变化。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142434JfVaP4jv2lbZF1pO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.71666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142434GQ9j3SMr8vPUW5gL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142435j1LnIWfK36lc9vb7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}